author: scottbw
msg: Added a HTML5 Geolocation widget; this is intended as a basic example widget which developers can build upon for making other location-based widgets. It works well in Chrome, OK in Safari and Firefox (browser bugs, not widget bugs - if it stops working, you have to close and open the window or browser).
Note the icon is CC Zero licensed from http://www.sjjb.co.uk/mapicons/ (this is in the SVG metadata)
